  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators aim to investigate and understand the circulating miRNA profiles after
      acute aneurysmal subarachnoid haemorrhage and underlying pathological significance.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      1. The investigators aim to investigate the miRNA classifier for delayed cerebral
           infarction after aneurysmal subarachnoid haemorrhage;

        2. The investigators aim to investigate the corresponding circulating and CSF miRNA
           profiles.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
